v17 server.route(route)

    route:
        path        required    the absolute path '/...'
        method      required     'GET', 'POST', 'PUT', 'PATCH', 'DELETE', or 'OPTIONS'.
        vhost       optional    a domain string or an array of domain strings 
        handler     required    function  : generate the response 
        options     optional    an object or a function 
        rules       optional    custom rules object. 